      "role": "user",
      "content": "i've been traveling for weeks now... seeing all these places i used to dream about. but honestly? i feel like i've reached the end of the map. there aren't any more roads left that feel worth walking. everything just feels so heavy and empty.",
      "source": "evaluator"
